USING AMIGADOS FOR BEGINNERS - THE GLOSSARY@{UB}@{UU}
@{JLEFT}
I have included a glossary of terms that can be accessed by clicking with
the left mouse button on highlighted words within the text of the articles.
An example of this is the word @{"Format" LINK "ADB:Misc/Glossary/Format"} mentioned earlier.

There is also an @{"index" LINK "ADB:Misc/Glossary/Main"} to the glossary items so that you can read them
at any time independently of the articles.


